original_title: Tammy Pescatelli's Way After School Special
overview: Tammy went back to her hometown and performed at her high school. It's easy to make strangers who found you in success laugh, but how about people who knew you before puberty? In an 80s flashback, this former captain of the cheerleaders became the most likely to make you laugh!
title: Tammy Pescatelli's Way After School Special
